    {
      "beat_id": "B01",
      "t_start": 0.0,
      "estimated_duration_s": 9.0,
      "narration_text": "A quantum bit can be spin-up, spin-down, or any superposition. How do you picture all the possible superpositions at once? Every one of them is a point on the surface of a sphere.",
