      "source_audio": "../vox-bloch-sphere/mp3/beat-B02.mp3"
    },
    {
      "beat_id": "B03",
      "t_start": 19.0,
      "estimated_duration_s": 9.0,
      "narration_text": "Four complex parameters. Normalization and global phase each remove one. Two free parameters. Why does that give a sphere, and what are the poles?",
