        "type": "CARD",
        "source": "own",
        "motion": "hold"
      },
      "card": {
        "kind": "question",
        "copy": "A qubit has 4 real parameters.\nNormalization removes 1. Global phase removes 1.\n2 remain. Why a sphere?",
