    {
      "beat_id": "B04",
      "t_start": 28.0,
      "estimated_duration_s": 10.0,
      "narration_text": "The two remaining free parameters are the polar angle theta and the azimuthal angle phi. They parametrize the sphere exactly. The state is cosine of theta-over-two times spin-up, plus e-to-the-i-phi times sine of theta-over-two times spin-down.",
